{"tid":758704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男人一生有14個砲友？英國研究：其實根本記不清","createTime":"2018-07-28T03:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T05:40:36.000Z","uid":122,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff60e977ecd7f6a8a5f068c812e99a390dd8688","tid":758704,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"男性與女性在記憶性伴侶數量有所差異！英國格拉斯哥大學（University of Glasgow）最新研究指出，男性並不會確切記得跟多少人上過床，女性則是會記得每個床伴，以平均性伴侶數量來說就有明顯差異，男性為14個床伴，女性則為7個床伴，但男性往往誇大其辭，事實上床伴數量是用猜的，「根本記不起來！」<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》報導，格拉斯哥大學調查英國1萬5162名英國公民，受訪者的年紀介於16歲到74歲之間，結果刊登於《性研究期刊》（Journal of Sex Research），研究發現男性平均性伴侶數量為14個，女性則為7個，而男性不記得確切的床伴數量，往往會誇大其辭用猜的，「因為其實根本記不起來」，因此高估床伴數量。<br />\n<br />\n而女性的平均床伴數則為7個，且都能將數量記得一清二楚，調查也發現女性易對「一夜情」感到羞恥，因此在算床伴數量時會一併排除，因而給出「較低」的數量。此外，接受此次調查的男性中，有17.5%認為發生一夜情「完全沒不對」，但有這樣想法的女性卻僅9.3%而已。"},{"pid":"a5504929b6becd07eae2ba7b81c850c30390c360","tid":758704,"uid":140831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"英國d研究到底係咪呃funding <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de946d316cf5c2d9e537a6aa4999352874343eb","tid":758704,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"連登平均值呢？"},{"pid":"0b4e21572764c00698d65f4b5738781d52c3cece","tid":758704,"uid":88887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3de946d316cf5c2d9e537a6aa4999352874343eb","tid":758704,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"連登平均值呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"負"},{"pid":"01f703ef0a3d36ba0affb39ba882ef6c7a4c6ee0","tid":758704,"uid":41245,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"a5504929b6becd07eae2ba7b81c850c30390c360","tid":758704,"uid":140831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"英國d研究到底係咪呃funding <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解咁多英國研究好似好廢？<br />\n因為華媒淨係識睇抄英文嘅報導，娛樂化個研究出嚟餵啲低質讀者<br />\n每日全世界都有好多研究出爐，大把嘢都有學術嘅breakthrough，但傳媒專係揀啲性呀、屎尿屁嘅研究出嚟講，噉咪啱晒啲冇知識嘅人嘅口味囉<br />\n所以話英國研究+台灣報導先係垃圾"},{"pid":"2589dedf44254dd88d136facfd9cff5e22554c94","tid":758704,"uid":123657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"英國公民先係。"},{"pid":"dd1ce080d0574bffda41bd5639b07d79966a703b","tid":758704,"uid":192046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"男女個結果差成一半<br />\n係咪姐係有一半男人係gay?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60181914dc7ef3d76fc2342424e3586b1cf030e","tid":758704,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:31:21.000Z","msg":"中國製造"},{"pid":"bc469bda5839f4571759dfb8d06c96d9e83d278d","tid":758704,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de946d316cf5c2d9e537a6aa4999352874343eb","tid":758704,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"連登平均值呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"2個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左手同右手"},{"pid":"f3e292b1d66c3efe4a1feaa901680de72edceb0a","tid":758704,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01f703ef0a3d36ba0affb39ba882ef6c7a4c6ee0","tid":758704,"uid":41245,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"a5504929b6becd07eae2ba7b81c850c30390c360","tid":758704,"uid":140831,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"英國d研究到底係咪呃funding <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解咁多英國研究好似好廢？<br />\n因為華媒淨係識睇抄英文嘅報導，娛樂化個研究出嚟餵啲低質讀者<br />\n每日全世界都有好多研究出爐，大把嘢都有學術嘅breakthrough，但傳媒專係揀啲性呀、屎尿屁嘅研究出嚟講，噉咪啱晒啲冇知識嘅人嘅口味囉<br />\n所以話英國研究+台灣報導先係垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"傳媒其實就係一個社會嘅廣泛教育者<br />\n想知一個地方嘅人文質素，睇吓佢嘅新聞同大眾娛樂劇集咩質素就知"},{"pid":"0045dd0172be796d3b488d125baaef5ec0d59133","tid":758704,"uid":6221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd1ce080d0574bffda41bd5639b07d79966a703b","tid":758704,"uid":192046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"男女個結果差成一半<br />\n係咪姐係有一半男人係gay?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"重睇啦好無"},{"pid":"d355e697514da1863ed3d4a63d9a3492a478c743","tid":758704,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd1ce080d0574bffda41bd5639b07d79966a703b","tid":758704,"uid":192046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"男女個結果差成一半<br />\n係咪姐係有一半男人係gay?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"調查也發現女性易對「一夜情」感到羞恥，因此在算床伴數量時會一併排除<br />\n<br />\n=女性每兩個床伴有一個係「一夜情」"}]}